# the matrix expands into a JVM row (app) and an sbt-snx native row (appNative)
# the JVM row compiles as a plain JVM project (its scalajvm/Platform.scala on the path)
> app/compile
# the native row compiles its scalanative/Platform.scala AND links a native binary through sbt-snx (snxLink is an
# sbt-snx-only task, so its success proves SNXPlugin drives the native row inside the matrix)
> appNative/Compile/snxLink
# and the linked native binary runs
> appNative/run
